dct_title_s: Map of a portion of the Miami River Basin at the Loramie and Mosquito Creek Area showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Miami River Basin (Loramie and Mosquito Creek Area)
dct_description_sm: Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Loramie and Mosquito Creek Area and quality of underground water.
Scale bar lower left corner of map.
"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water"
Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
